  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV56">
<l>viyaliṭa muṇṭa pirāṉār viṭutta tiruvaruḷā</l>
<l>luyaliṭam peṟṟuynta mañcalan tōḻiyōr taṇṭeṉṟalvan</l>
<l>tayaliṭai yāru maṟintila rampūn tuḻāyiṉiṉtēṉ</l>
<l>puyaluṭai nīrmaiyi ṉāṟṟaṭa viṟṟeṉ pulaṉkalaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having obtained a place for escaping by the sacred grace emitted by the lord</l>
<l>who had eaten the wide area we have escaped, we’re not afraid, friend. Nobody</l>
<l>in the neighbourhood knows of a cool south wind’s coming [and] stroking the vessel</l> 
<l>of my senses with the moist essence of the sweet honey of pretty-flowered Tulsi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
